Class Variable

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Variable

  •  class Variable
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Barry Warnock Variable is the class that will represent our IDIOT variables, each Variable tracks its name, its value, and whether or not it has been initialized yet
